lead_paragraph: Former England and Manchester United defender Gary Neville is not targeting a long-term career in management and says he is "relaxed" about how long he stays at the helm of Spanish side Valencia.

headline.print_headline: Management Not My Long-Term Goal, Says Neville
headline.main: Management Not My Long-Term Goal, Says Neville
